rbnBulkStatsMIB.name: rbnBulkStatsMIB

revisions.description: Added a new table rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrTable, to accommodate the Multi-Instance Bulkstats feature. Also obsoleted the old objects.
Initial version. This version includes objects for notifying the failure of bulk statistics data transfer only.

rbnBulkStatsMIB.contactinfo: RedBack Networks, Inc. Postal: 300 Holger Way San Jose, CA 95134-1362 USA Phone: +1 408 750 3500 Fax: +1 408 750 3599 E-mail: mib-info@redback.com
rbnBulkStatsMIB.description: The MIB used to generically manage Bulk Statistics Gathering functionality on RedBack Networks devices.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddrType.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddrType
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddrType.description: The address type contained in rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr.description: The IP Address of the receiver station to which transfer of bulk statistics data was last attempted. If the IP address type is unknown, or if no transfers have occured, a zero-length string will be returned.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrStatus.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrStatus
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrStatus.description: The status of the last bulk statistics data transfer.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrTable.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrTable
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrTable.description: A table which is used to monitor the last attempted transfer of the bulk statistics data for each bulkstats policy. All rows in this table are accessible when the context 'local' is specified in the snmp message. Snmp requests using other contexts shall return only the row which matches the context.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrEntry.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrEntry
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrEntry.description: An entry that indicates the status of the last attempted transfer of the bulk statistics data for each policy.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddrType2.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddrType2
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddrType2.description: The address type contained in rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr2.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr2.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr2
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrIpAddr2.description: The IP Address of the receiver station to which transfer of bulk statistics data was last attempted. If the IP address type is unknown, or if no transfers have occured, a zero-length string will be returned.

rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrStatus2.name: rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrStatus2
rbnBulkStatsLastTrfrStatus2.description: The status of the last bulk statistics data transfer.

rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail.name: rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail
rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail.description: A rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail notification signifies that there has been a failure in the transfer of the bulk statistics data onto the receiver.

rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail2.name: rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail2
rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail2.description: A rbnBulkStatsTrfrFail2 notification signifies that there has been a failure in the transfer of the bulk statistics data onto the receiver.

rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup.name: rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup
rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup.description: A collection of objects providing bulk statistics transfer information. The rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup is mandatory when the rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup is implemented.

rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup.name: rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup
rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup.description: A collection of notifications providing Bulk Statistics transfer information.

rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup2.name: rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup2
rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup2.description: A collection of objects providing bulk statistics transfer information. The rbnBulkStatsMIBObjectGroup2 is mandatory when the rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup2 is implemented.

rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup2.name: rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup2
rbnBulkStatsMIBNotificationGroup2.description: A collection of notifications providing Bulk Statistics transfer failure information.

rbnBulkStatsMIBCompliance.name: rbnBulkStatsMIBCompliance
rbnBulkStatsMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for the BulkStats MIB

rbnBulkStatsMIBCompliance2.name: rbnBulkStatsMIBCompliance2
rbnBulkStatsMIBCompliance2.description: The compliance statement for the BulkStats MIB
